    <CS_Studio_Prop_Shader>Shader</CS_Studio_Prop_Shader>
    <CS_Studio_Prop_Shader_Tooltip>Determines how the layer handles transparency and depth:
• Cutout: Hard edges, writes depth (standard for vanilla pawn layers/apparel).
• CutoutComplex: Hard edges with secondary color mask support.
• Transparent: Soft semi-transparent edges, no depth (use for glasses, glowing effects, veils).
• TransparentPostLight: Like Transparent but unaffected by shadows.
• MetaOverlay: For special technical passes.</CS_Studio_Prop_Shader_Tooltip>
    <CS_Studio_Prop_CustomShaderPath>Custom Shader Path</CS_Studio_Prop_CustomShaderPath>
