    <CS_Studio_Prop_Alpha>Opacity</CS_Studio_Prop_Alpha>
    <CS_Studio_Prop_Alpha_Tooltip>Controls the transparency of this layer. 1 = fully opaque, 0 = fully transparent. Only available for transparent shaders.</CS_Studio_Prop_Alpha_Tooltip>
    <CS_Studio_Prop_ZWrite>Depth Write</CS_Studio_Prop_ZWrite>
    <CS_Studio_Prop_ZWrite_Tooltip>When enabled, this transparent layer writes to the depth buffer, allowing other transparent objects to correctly occlude behind it. Useful for semi-transparent equipment that should block visibility of body parts behind it.</CS_Studio_Prop_ZWrite_Tooltip>
    <CS_Studio_Prop_MaskTexPath>Mask Texture Path</CS_Studio_Prop_MaskTexPath>
    <CS_Studio_Prop_MaskTexPath_Tooltip>Optional mask texture that controls per-pixel transparency. White = fully opaque, Black = fully transparent. The mask color multiplies with the main texture alpha.</CS_Studio_Prop_MaskTexPath_Tooltip>
